# This repository is LF-only. Without this, a Windows checkout (GitHub runners
# default to core.autocrlf=true) rewrites committed text files to CRLF. That breaks
# the byte-exact codegen idempotence gate — the embedded generated/*.json are
# rendered with LF, but read back from a CRLF working tree — and would smuggle \r
# into the `include_str!`-embedded IR/docs on any Windows build.
* text=auto eol=lf
